---
import { site } from '../../config/site';
---

<section id="lavori" class="py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20 bg-zinc-900 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-white/10"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-white/10"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_80%_50%,#bf282b15,transparent)]"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <p class="text-brand text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-3">Portfolio</p>
    <h2 class="text-white text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-5 sm:mb-6">I nostri lavori</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base">
      Migliaia di traslochi, centinaia di famiglie e aziende che ci hanno affidato le loro cose più care.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8 sm:mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base">
      Guarda le nostre foto su Facebook: vedrai come trattiamo casa tua con la stessa cura che riserveresti tu.
    </p>

    <a
      href={site.social.facebook}
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-colors duration-200 w-full sm:w-auto"
    >
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path>
      </svg>
      Guarda i nostri lavori su Facebook
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
